pageContext.claim: “The Fake News said I played golf today, and I did NOT! I had meeting in various locations, while closely monitoring the U.S. Embassy situation in Iraq, which I am still doing. The Corrupt Lamestream Media knew this but, not surprisingly, failed to report or correct!”
pageContext.analysis: The White House pool report merely said Trump arrived at Trump International Golf Club in West Palm Beach at 10:46 a.m. The motorcade left the golf course 49 minutes later. Trump did not explain why he drove to his golf course but did not play a round.
